name: The Shades Of Someone's Inner Self
description: About 3 feelings in 1 soul. A person who lives with his anger and grudges in the past and continues to try to accept and forgive all his bitter and cruel past within himself. However, reality said otherwise, He thought it would be easy to accept all this, but it turned out to be wrong. The voices that often haunt him and his soul always come back and make him come back to life with 3 feelings that torment him
